<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink228-kilavi">talaimakaṉ varaivu vēṇṭiviṭat tamar maṟuttuḻi yavar kēṭkumāṟṟāṉ ṟalaimakaṭkuc colluvāḷāyt tōḻi yaṟattoṭu niṉṟatu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante standing with virtue; [the confidante] who spoke to the heroine in a manner [the hero] could hear, when [her] people refused as the hero requested [for her hand in] marriage. 
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink228">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nammūr</l>
<l>nirantilaṅ karuviya neṭumalai nāṭa</l>
<l>ṉirantukuṟai yuṟāaṉ peyari</l>
<l>ṉeṉṉā vatukoṉam miṉṉuyir nilaiyē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
  <l>  Alas, O friend— </l>
  <l rend="space">if the man from the town upon the tall mountain, </l>
  <l>with waterfalls that spread and gleam, </l>
  <l rend="space">should depart as one whose request is denied, after entreating,   </l>
  <l>what will become the state of our sweet life? </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
